{
  "_readme": [
    "Tone3000 API keys. OPTIONAL: the app ships with a working publishable key",
    "(T3kConfig.EmbeddedPublishableKey), so sign-in needs no setup. This file only",
    "OVERRIDES it - copy it to %APPDATA%\\Namager\\tone3000.json to point the app at",
    "your own tone3000.com developer registration.",
    "publishable_key (t3k_pub_...): the OAuth client_id.",
    "secret_key (t3k_cs_...): OPTIONAL. The app NEVER reads it - it exists only for the",
    "  dev probe tool (tools/T3kProbe). Treat it like a password; never commit it.",
    "redirect_port: 0 = pick any free port for the OAuth loopback redirect. Set a fixed",
    "  port only if your Tone3000 app registration requires an exact redirect URI."
  ],
  "publishable_key": "t3k_pk_YOUR_KEY_HERE",
  "secret_key": "",
  "redirect_port": 0
}
